minkowski <- function(x, y, p = 2) {
  if ((p < Inf) & (p > 0)) {
    s <- sum(abs(x - y)^p)^(1/p)
  } 
  else if (p == Inf) {
       s <- max(abs(x - y))
  } 
  return(s)
}

dist.matriz.minkowski <- function(M, p = 2) {
  n <- dim(M)[1]
  m <- dim(M)[2]  
  D <- matrix(0,nrow=n,ncol=n)
  for (i in 1:n) {
    for (j in 1:n) {
      D[i,j] <- minkowski(Datos[i,],Datos[j,], p)
    }
  }
  rownames(D)<-rownames(M)
  colnames(D)<-rownames(M)
  return(as.dist(D))
}
